  "detailed_description": "You were accused and found guilty of temporal crimes, crimes against time that you did not commit. Sentenced to 10,000 millennia in the cells of Chronos, the thought of impending madness weighed heavily on you. But, perhaps there's a glimmer of hope. Those foolish Chronosians didn't find your trusty stopwatch. Armed with your timepiece, there may be a way out of here...<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BREAK FREE</h2>Stop the stopwatch at exactly 1 second, earn gold and find freedom. But be warned, time is not something to be played with lightly. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1953800/extras/40b8f3a7a0f96ca2a4c99c18f686c40d.poster.avif?t=1741007022\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1953800/extras/40b8f3a7a0f96ca2a4c99c18f686c40d.mp4?t=1741007022\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >UPGRADE, UPGRADE, UPGRADE</h2>With thousands of upgrades, you'll earn your freedom in no time.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1953800/extras/e4bda7ba0ec33f3d31a1994182fd4588.apng?t=1741007022\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1953800/extras/e4bda7ba0ec33f3d31a1994182fd4588.poster.avif?t=1741007022\" class=\"bb_img\" width=614 height=303 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >PROVE YOUR WORTH</h2>Prove your worth and earn badges by completing 20 difficult challenges.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1953800/extras/505f94bf43aaa3a93c14ad0f63271208.apng?t=1741007022\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1953800/extras/505f94bf43aaa3a93c14ad0f63271208.poster.avif?t=1741007022\" class=\"bb_img\" width=614 height=80 /></picture></span>",
